April 19 in Columbus 
Columbus 2 New England 2. Goals: Grabavoy (Virtuoso, Ngwenya) 8, Kamara (Hejduk, Evans) 86; Dorman (Cristman) 10, Twellman 38.
Columbus - Gruenebaum, Hejduk, Gonzalez, Hendrickson, Pierce, Ngwenya (Kamara, 69), Grabavoy, O'Rourke, Gaven, Herron, Virtuoso (Evans, 62). 
New England - Reis, Heaps, Riley, John, Ralston, Dorman, Joseph, Larentowicz, Smith (Thompson, 60), Twellman, Cristman (Noonan, 66). 
Yellow Cards: Columbus - Grabavoy 49, Hejduk 82, Pierce 94+; New England - Heaps 42, Larentowicz 76. 
Referee: Ricardo Salazar. 
Att.: 13,290. 

April 21 in East Rutherford, N.J. 
New York 1 Houston 0. Goal: Altidore (Freeman) 60. 
New York - Waterreus, Freeman, Mendes, Parke, Dunivant, Richards (Stammler, 54), Kovalenko, Reyna, van den Bergh (Vide, 91+), Altidore (Wolyniec, 74), Mathis. 
Houston - Onstad, Cochrane, Gray, Robinson, Barrett, Mullan, Clark, De Rosario, Davis (Mulrooney, 70), Dalglish (Wondolowski, 73), Moreno (Ching, 69). 
Yellow Cards: New York - Parke 48; Houston - De Rosario 10, Robinson 63. 
Red Card: New York - Mathis 36. 
Referee: Baldomero Toledo. 
Att.: 12,481. 

April 21 in Bridgeview, Ill. 
Chicago 2 Kansas City 1. Goals: Barrett (Armas, Rolfe) 36, Rolfe pen. 73; Marinelli pen. 90. 
Chicago - Pickens, Segares, Curtin, Brown, Robinson, Armas, Guerrero, Mapp (Carr, 55), Gutierrez, Rolfe (Telesford,91+), Barrett (Thiago, 86). 
Kansas City - Hartman, Burciaga Jr., Conrad, Garcia, Jewsbury (Pore, 79), Harrington, Arnaud, Victorine, Zavagnin, Movsisyan (Marinelli, 46), Johnson. 
Yellow Cards: Chicago - Curtin 24;?Kansas City - Garcia 5. 
Referee: Kevin Stott. 
Att.: 11,717. 

April 21 in Carson, Calif. 
Chivas USA 4 Real Salt Lake 0. Goals: Galindo (Zotinca) 1, Galindo (Zotinca, Kljestan) 9, Razov (Mendoza, Galindo) 43, Taylor 89. 
Chivas USA - Guzan, Zotinca (Hernandez, 78), Suarez, Vaughn, Bornstein, Kljestan, Guevara, Marsch, Mendoza, Galindo (Taylor, 66), Razov (Cunliffe, 65). 
Real Salt Lake - Rimando, Stewart (Brown, 72), Pope, Torres, Forko, Klein, Ballouchy, Kreis, Talley, Adu, Cunningham. 
Yellow Cards: Chivas USA - Galindo 25, Marsch 68, Kljestan 76. 
Referee: Hilario Grajeda. 
Att.: 11,253. 

April 22 in Frisco, Texas 
FC Dallas 3 Colorado 1. Goals: Nunez (McCarty) 29, Nunez 78, Oduro (Cooper) 93+; Kirovski (Cooke) 34. 
FC Dallas - Hislop, Moor, Goodson, Yi, Gbandi, McCarty (Rhine, 88), Nunez (Alvarez, 81), Pitchkolan, Toja, Cooper, Ruiz (Oduro, 68). 
Colorado - Coundoul, Prideaux (Gargan, 33), Ihemelu, Petke (Casey, 81), Vanney, Cooke, Beckerman, Mastroeni, Gomez, Hernandez, Kirovski (Peterson, 67). 
Yellow Cards: FC Dallas - Ruiz 26, Moor 58, Goodson 59, Pitchkolan 61; Colorado - Beckerman 7, Mastroeni 77. 
Referee: Ricardo Salazar. 
Att.: 20,500.
